For the ``classical'' Cox model \code{mlt_GBSG2_1}, the standard errors
of all three methods applied (\cmd{coxph}, \cmd{mlt}, \cmd{flexsurvspline})
are more or less identical 
<<GBSG2-1-coxph-cmpr>>=  
